00:18:09.955 --> 00:18:14.955
And I did it for all of the relevant users that it found in the prior request.


85
00:18:14.955 --> 00:18:33.955
So this was a pretty good success case, and I think what also made it successful is that there was a hunter that was driving it with a very concrete playbook. Um, so the agent was doing a lot of the searching and the data analysis, but the hunt was kind of defined, or the playbook was defined by the expert in this case.


