00:18:33.955 --> 00:18:58.955
Last thing I wanted to show is some of our reasoning transparency. So, basically, it's a little bit dense, but these are the requests that were sent to the sub-agent, so it called the AWS agent once, and the Datadog agent numerous number of times to really do that iterative refinement. So it's both Datadog agent calling the Datadog MCP a bunch of times, and the orchestrator agent calling the Datadog agent a bunch of times. So there's two loops here.


87
00:18:58.955 --> 00:19:04.955
We also ran an A-B testing week in the same AWS Privilege escalation Hunt Week.


88
00:19:04.955 --> 00:19:15.955
Team A utilize the hunting co-pilot, and Team B was a more experienced threat hunter, could not use the hunting co-pilot, but they could use ChatGPT, it didn't make sense to cut out AI usage entirely.


89
00:19:15.955 --> 00:19:22.955
We tracked live metrics for the tool, but we also had them fill out rubrics and questionnaires for subjective scoring.


90
00:19:22.955 --> 00:19:44.955
There were many hypotheses explored during this week, so we reviewed the results holistically and compared similar hypotheses. This is because we wanted to minimize testing disruption for their hunts, like, these are actual production hunts, and they're expected to deliver results from these. When we compared the results of the two teams, we found that the hunting co-pilot cut the average query iteration time from 10 minutes to five minutes.


91
00:19:44.955 --> 00:19:57.955
And the hunt duration for each of these hypotheses were about 60 minutes, and the tool helped save 25 of those minutes. We also noticed that the response times all remained under 6 minutes for this week in particular.


92
00:19:57.955 --> 00:20:12.955
When we looked at the subjective scores, the tool succeeded in hypothesis relevancy and context awareness. It stayed on track, and it used the data to drive conclusions. However, on more complex hypotheses, where a lot of data needed to be analyzed, it struggled with signal-to-noise control.


93
00:20:12.955 --> 00:20:20.955
