00:20:37.955 --> 00:20:54.955
We garnered a deeper understanding of the automation boundary and how we can help our hunters. Currently, our automation boundary is threefold. In addition to query generation and data analysis, our hunters also wanted the agent to pull in different sources and pivot on these hypotheses.


